description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Yulenka purrs with a rating of 28, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 140, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 5 for East, Box for South, and Stringalong for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [140 Votes, Top 15% Score]
